Description: CVE-2026-56370 - validate object indices in ConnectedComponentsImage
 ConnectedComponentsImage() in magick/vision.c could write past the end of
 the per-object array when a user-supplied artifact (e.g.
 connected-components:keep-ids, :remove-ids, :keep-top) referenced an object
 id outside the [0, component_image->colors) range. The unchecked indices
 led to out-of-bounds writes into the object[] array.
 .
